 5/2/18 Sell Walk down to " B" Coy who are some distanc out of the villag along the pleasantest seclud countri lane which must be love in the Spring . Found most of the men engag on make a miniatur rifl rang Later the doctor came down and gave a lectur on VD. Just close to the town is an old burn down chateau . After lunch rode around the billet and inspect the Transport line and the Signal School and the School of Instruction . After mess went to BdeHd saw the Gener ( Paton ) arrang matter re P.V. Martin and other . He goe on leav in the morn leav me in charg . On return hand everyth over to Matthew and did a lot of write . A sore throat and a bad cold just like befor go on leav last . Rotten
